body:
# [Click to download latest binary] (https://github.com/mazong1123/infopathanalyzer/releases/download/1.5/InfoPath.Analyzer.1.5.zip)

### What's InfoPath Analyzer?
It's a tool to show the inside of an InfoPath template. It allows you to search fields across all InfoPath views, show tree hierarchy across views, and etc.

### Contribute
Contribution is always welcome. Please find source code at [GitHub](https://github.com/mazong1123/infopathanalyzer/).

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with InfoPath Analyzer? File an issue on [GitHub](https://github.com/mazong1123/infopathanalyzer/issues).
